/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-005/judgments/chain-02.md:33:This lands cleanly. Once a mechanism is promoted, the chain should already be able to write the candidate inequality, transfer estimate, or contradiction line where the mechanism enters. Otherwise the route has not crossed from interpretation to proof pressure. The refined chain now requires an explicit candidate inequality in Step 3.
