+- [VERIFIED] `step-009/GOAL.md` requires one exact theorem endpoint, one
+  contradiction line, one literal cash-out, one progress currency, one minimum
+  threshold, and admission rules before any tensor packaging or observable
+  screening can count as progress.
+- [VERIFIED] `decision-013.md` invalidates the prior compactness-rigidity chain
+  because Step 1 failed to freeze one coherent framework-endpoint-temporal
+  ledger.
+- [VERIFIED] `decision-014.md` activates run `run-006` only on the stricter
+  condition that Step 1 first freeze one endpoint-complete ledger and kill the
+  branch immediately if that cannot be done concretely.
